videos.description: Auburn guard Malik Dunbar swats a UAB layup attempt off the backboard, then dunks an alley-oop pass from Bryce Brown at the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's Dunbar blocks shot, slams down alley-oop) 2018/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Dunbar blocks shot, slams down alley-oop

videos.description: Danjel Purifoy gets an offensive rebound and goes up for the and-1 in his first game since a suspension back in March.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's Purifoy makes and-1 in 1st game since March) 2018/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Purifoy makes and-1 in 1st game since March

videos.description: Zack Bryant finds Jalen Perry all alone in the corner and he buries a 3-pointer to give UAB a lead over Auburn in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UAB takes 2nd-half lead with Perry's 3-pointer) 2018/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: UAB takes 2nd-half lead with Perry's 3-pointer

videos.description: Jared Harper drives and lobs it to Chuma Okeke for a powerful two-handed slam to extend Auburn's lead late in the second half vs. UAB.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's Okeke throws down alley-oop) 2018/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Okeke throws down alley-oop

videos.description: UAB gets an offensive rebound and Jeremiah Bell nails a 3-pointer in the final seconds, sending the game to overtime vs. Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UAB's game-tying 3 sends it to OT) 2018/12/15 ESHEET
